<paragraph id="180F6D434E7AD2FA5C51DE7E7D301E3D" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
BOLIVIA. Cochabamba, Espirito Santo, 
<emphasis id="E533B19F88DE84FDB2FFF8882A81E1CF" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">M. Bang</emphasis>
